Computational Screening of Nanoporous Materials for Hexane and Heptane Isomer Separation
Yongchul G. Chung,†,§,■ Peng Bai,⊥,■ Maciej Haranczyk,# Karson T. Leperi,† Peng Li,‡
Hongda Zhang,† Timothy C. Wang,‡ Tim Duerinck,†,∥ Fengqi You,□ Joseph T. Hupp,‡,●
