where rij is the distance between sites i and j, and σ and ε are the LJ
well-depth and size parameters. LJ parameters for sites of different
types were computed using the Lorentz−Berthelot29 combining rules. Adsorbate−adsorbate and adsorbate−zeolite interactions were truncated at 14 Å with analytical tail-corrections applied for interactions
Chemistry of Materials Article
